13 AUTHOR: Add the following House Coauthors: Wolfley and Rosecrants
14 AMENDMENT NO. 1. Page 1, restore the title to read
15 “An Act relating to postsecondary education; waiving
tuition for the spouse or children of a Gold Star
16 recipient; amending 70 O.S. 2021, Section 3218.7-1,
as amended by Section 2, Chapter 382, O.S.L. 2024 (70
17 O.S. Supp. 2025, Section 3218.7-1), which relates to
waiver of room and board fees; expanding application
18 of waiver to the spouse or children of a Gold Star
recipient; amending 70 O.S. 2021, Section 14-134,
19 which relates to waiver of tuition at career
technology districts; waiving tuition and fees for
20 the spouse or children of a Gold Star recipient;
amending Section 3, Chapter 382, O.S.L. 2024 (70 O.S.
21 Supp. 2025, Section 14-134.1), which relates to
waiver of fees at career technology districts;
22 waiving fees for the spouse or children of a Gold
Star recipient; providing for noncodification;
23 providing for codification; and providing an
effective date.”
